The Block Australia Fans vs Faves Series 8 Episode 50

The Block is back with a Fans versus Favorites format - will the old hands prevail?

Its a busy time on The Block with the terraces nearing completion. Scotty and Shelley pay the teams one last on site visit before they complete their renovation and life on a building site is uncomfortable for everyone as heatwave sets in.
